hen I usually play) the knight should still be able to tank the PoP mobs that hit for massive dmg although they will need to be healed a little more than the warrior but at least give us knights a  chance without making the cleric  go 0om every three kills. Im sure I will get flamed for some of the things I have said, I just want equal opportunity for all melee or hybrid classes or at least close to it so knights dont get thrown to the side once again. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Doene Laforge</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
